 Destructor leaped over the hill. He had been watching from afar for a long 
time. He attacked Nightlight from behind with six shots at her back.

Galavatron hovered in the distance. Watching the battle. He knew proto and 
Destructor. Rodimus Prime made his blood boil. That was a fight he couldnt 
wait the have. To crush his spark would be a wonderful achievement.
